name: report order
query:
select
`tabReport Order`.nama_pelanggan as "Nama Member:data:20",
`tabReport Order`.status as "status:select:100" ,
`tabReport Order`.harga as "harga:Int:100",
`tabReport Order`.potongan_harga as "diskon:Int:100",
`tabReport Order`.total_harga as "total harga:Int:100",
`tabReport Order`.jml_cash as "pembayaran:Int:100",
`tabReport Order`.kembalian as "Kembalian:Int:100"  
from `tabReport Order`
